  "name": "Curious Spirit",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 4th level, the soul weaver may expend one soul to commune with the spirit world, allowing her to speak with and question the ancestral dead. This allows her to attempt a single Knowledge check, even if untrained, and with an insight bonus equal to her soul weaver level + her casting ability modifier. This may be used to reroll a Knowledge check the soul weaver had previously failed, but no more than once per question. If the soul weaver is touching a body that has been dead for no longer than 1 day per level, she may summon and speak with that body&#8217;s spirit for up to 1 minute per caster level, which retains all knowledge it had in life but is under no obligation to talk or answer any questions.</p>\n",
